# Runtime config stores — keep secrets-bearing settings out of git even if a user
# points DATA_PATH at the repo (see docs/SETUP-AND-CONFIG.md § Security posture).
# The out-of-checkout default (~/.anime-app) is the primary defense; these are
# belt-and-suspenders.
/settings.json
/config.json

__pycache__/
*.pyc


docs/rag

